outlsd: usage: outlsd p
p = 1: bond lists
p = 2: ARGOS format (obsolete format)
p = 3: JMNMOL format (obsolete format)
p = 4: Ye Olde MACROMODEL format (obsolete format)
p = 5: SMILES chains
p = 6: LSD 2D DRAW format (.coo)
p = 7: SDF 2D format (.mol)
p = 8: SDF 3D format without H atoms (.mol)
p = 9: SDF 3D format with H atoms (.mol)
